flowchart TD
    Build[Build Java Lambda JAR] --> Network[Deploy Network Stack]
    Network --> Database[Deploy Database Stack]
    Database --> Migration[Deploy Migration Stack]
    Migration --> RunMigration[Run Flyway Migration Task]
    RunMigration --> Lambda[Deploy Lambda Stack]
    Lambda --> Cognito[Deploy Cognito Stack]
    Cognito --> Api[Deploy API Stack]
    Api --> Monitoring[Deploy Monitoring Stack]

